               returning from transportation, and being found at large on the <rs id="t17830910-21-cd114" type="crimeDate">15th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830910-21-off113 t17830910-21-cd114"></join> last, without any lawful cause
